<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV40">
<l>kōlap pakaṟkaḷi ṟoṉṟukaṟ puyyak kuḻāmvirinta</l>
<l>nīlakkaṅ kuṟkaḷi ṟellā niṟaintaṉa nēriḻaiyīr</l>
<l>ñālappoṉ mātiṉ maṇāḷaṉ tuḻāynaṅkaḷ cūḻkuḻaṟkē</l>
<l>yēlap puṉainteṉṉai māremmai nōkkuva teṉṟukolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When the beautiful elephant bull of day vanishes behind the stones,</l>
<l>spread in a crowd all elephant bulls pervaded the blue night, you with fine jewels.</l>
<l>Adorning suitably our surrounding curls with the Tulsi from the bridegroom</l>
<l>of the earth- and the gold-woman, when will our people look at us?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
